article_title: Volga, SD Man Dies In Rollover Crash In Minnesota
article_text:
Scott Co., MN

A man from Volga died in a rollover crash south of Marystown, Minnesota Saturday afternoon.

51-year-old Andrew Bennett was headed south on Highway 169 around 4 p.m. Saturday when he lost control of his vehicle, entered the median and rolled.

No other vehicles were involved in the crash, and Bennett was the only passenger in the vehicle.
